Growth<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto'><span
lang=EN style='font-family:Montserrat;mso-ansi-language:EN'>Currently pursuing
a Bachelor of Science in Leadership and Management at Rutgers Business School,
graduating May 2029. Fluent in Greek with advanced technical and business
expertise. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

